### GET all poems
GET {{url}}/poems
Accept: application/json

### GET a single poem
GET {{url}}/poem/1
Content-Type: : application/json
Accept: application/json



### POST example
POST {{url}}/poem
Content-Type: : application/json
Accept: application/json

{
"title" : "The Night Shift" ,
   "poem" :"A haiku reflecting a coder’s late-night debugging session, where errors persist but determination shines until dawn." ,
   "style" : "Haiku"
    }





